%% SIEM-ish signal flow (sanitized)
sequenceDiagram
  participant App as App/IDP
  participant Cribl as Cribl Stream
  participant Splunk as Splunk (Index)
  participant SOAR as SOAR/Ticketing

  App->>Cribl: auth logs (success/fail)
  Cribl->>Cribl: redact tokens + normalize fields
  Cribl->>Splunk: send via HEC (index=<INDEX>)
  Splunk->>Splunk: correlation searches + notable events
  Splunk->>SOAR: webhook / incident creation
